---
title: Sausage Pepper Pasta for Dinner with Sausage Sub Sandwiches for Lunch
description: Cook it once, eat it twice: tonight’s dinner extras transform into tomorrow’s lunch. That’s thanks to special added ingredients that can easily be heated up, even at the office (your coworkers will be amazed, trust us). This particular 2-in-1 recipe is an Italian-American power combo that works sausage and bell pepper into both the hearty penne pasta dinner and the sub-style sandwich for lunch. The nutrition facts panel represents the nutrient values for the Sausage Pepper Pasta Dinner.
